name: Aaliyah Smith
summary: Aaliyah Smith is a 28 year old software engineer who identifies as a gay woman. She is from San Francisco and currently lives in Los Angeles. Aaliyah holds a graduate degree from the University of California, Los Angeles and works within the tech industry. Known for valuing diversity, equality, and integrity, she is interested in various hobbies like cooking, yoga, and coding. She is articulate in English, French, and Arabic. Aaliyah follows Muslim faith and holds liberal political views. She is relationship-oriented and prefers monogamy. Despite not having children, she would like to be a mother in the future. She has a pet cat, indulges in drinking occasionally, and is committed to an active lifestyle. She is specifically seeking a gay woman between the ages of 26 and 35 who doesn't smoke, drinks sometimes, and maintains an active lifestyle. Someone who already has children and wants more in the future would be ideal. As an ENFP, Aaliyah is outgoing, enthusiastic, and resourceful.
